* RESTful APIs

- Semantic organization of endpoints (paths) and methods

Example: get ebird observations for a time range

	Method: GET
	Path: /observations
	Query Parameters: start=date, end=date

	https://ebird.boisestate.edu/observations?start=2018-10-03&end=2018-11-08

* RESTful APIs

Example: get ebird observations for a time range within some bounding box

	Method: GET
	Path: /observations
	Query Parameters: start=date, end=date, minx=number, maxx=number, miny=number, maxy=number

	https://ebird.boisestate.edu/observations?start=2018-10-03&end=2018-11-08&
	minx=-116.051161&maxx=-116.0054645&miny=45.45464&maxy=45.865411


